Name: 0861 Sink Strainer Basket Corner Kitchen Triangular Multi functional Drain Shelf
Description:
Sink Strainer Basket Corner Kitchen Triangular Multi functional Drain Shelf

 

Novel flute design and considerate drain holes can exactly let soap drain and dry naturally. The back side has water ripple design can not collects the water. Keeps your house clean and dry. No Mushy Soap. Optimizes the lifespan of your soap.
Suitable for All Styles of bathrooms, shower, kitchens, laundry, sink, workshops, and counter tops. The soap holder has a self-draining levels. Put the soap box right on the edge of the sink, the water will drip into the sink and keep your soap dry and make it last longer.

Features :

  • Triangular Storage Holder Design-The triangular storage rack makes full use of the space of sink, the curve edge makes it fit corners of your kitchen sink well, space-efficient design keeps your kitchen organized, enjoying comfortable and spacious
  • Hollow Design-Drain basket hollow design at the bottom is great ideals for draining or drying small kitchen items. Make it easy to be as a storage holder for fruits and food, doubles as to store debris without clogging the sewer as a sink garbage basket. Strainer basket surface also has a certain flat space which is customized to place dish washing sponges, cleaning balls, soap, etc.
  • Safe And Tough Material-Sink Strainers Basket is made of thick PP materials which is rather durable, dry quickly, non toxic and healthy, not easy to break
  • Easy to Install: Thick PP material, no punching, no sticking, sticking firmly, do not hurt the wall. The kitchen sink strainer basket can be installed in the bathroom, kitchen and other tiles, smooth wall.
  • Strong Suction Sucker Design: The suction sucker is firm without leaving traces. It is easy to disassemble and has a strong load-bearing capacity. Small objects can be placed in the kitchen multipurpose basket.

Name: 7255 Nail Cutter for Every Age Group (1pc)
Description:
Personal Care Stainless Steel professional Large size Nail Cutter Clipper

The practical build of this nail clipper saves you from applying excessive force. It comes with a reinforced lever that makes it highly functional and easy to use.
The nail clipper is designed for your comfort. It is enclosed with a nail file and grime remover to help shape the nails and get rid of trapped grim and debris easily.

Robust Body

The clipper body is made of high carbon stainless steel hence it is very durable. Its body is lightweight and resistant to impact and abrasion.

Cut, Clean and File

Maintain and properly groom your nails with this robust and sharp grooming tool.

Nail Catcher

A polypropylene nail catcher is provided to prevent nail chips from flying. It can be used to collect nails and dispose them hygienically.

Reinforced Lever

The lever is made of reinforced Nylon and the lever cover is made of ABS resin. This nail clipper is built to provide enduring and effortless performance.
